g.text: Asks to update an allergy entry in the patient's medical record
Makes Http Request to get Medical History data
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDV
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Displays the fetched data and asks for the new data
Sends the new data(Allergies) to be updated
Makes Http Request to update an allergy entry in the patient's medical record
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDV
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Validates the data and updates the patient's medical record
